data.description: Beautiful Scenic gated community, one of a kind, with wooded views and views of lake Simms, the home is very upgraded, including Screen patio with pergola, new laminate floors ( water resistant and anti- scratch floors), no rugs in the house, Solar panels, fenced patio with no neighboors on the rear of the home. Is a single family one story with open floorplan immaculate conditions . Enjoy the amenities of the community with a resort-style swimming pool and tot lot, walking trails, playground, clubhouse, park and more.
